@startuml US_2.2.10_SSD
autonumber

actor "Shipping Agent\nRepresentative" as Agent
participant ":System" as System

== View All My VVNs ==
activate Agent
Agent -> System: Acede à secção "My Vessel Visits"
activate System
System --> Agent: Apresenta lista de todas as VVNs do agent com status
deactivate System

== View Single VVN Status ==
Agent -> System: Seleciona uma VVN da lista
activate System
System --> Agent: Apresenta detalhes completos da VVN (status, vessel, dates, cargo, crew, dock assignment)
deactivate System
deactivate Agent

@enduml
